{"tid":2116096,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果X檔案】上市商會造勢拆2%限制 疑鋪路李嘉誠大手買長實","createTime":"2020-07-20T03:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T03:00:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a7774dcbd26b782d8f9499c5e22bc347331240","tid":2116096,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"香港上市公司商會近日不斷吹風，建議放寬大股東動用私人資金回購公司股份，暫緩2%增購限制。《蘋果》翻查該商會背景，發現多為李嘉誠及其親信成員，再統計多名大孖沙過去12個月增持旗下公司概況，當中以李嘉誠近年增持長實（1113）比例逼近2%最高，種種迹象似為日後大手買入長實拆牆鬆綁鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n根據證監會《公司收購及合併守則》，持股量介乎30%至50%的上市公司股東，每12個月最多增持旗下公司股份不多於2%，否則須作出全面要約⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200720/CLIQ5QRLZJ4R6XUU4MQIXTFR3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200720%2FCLIQ5QRLZJ4R6XUU4MQIXTFR3U%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zXf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=84c7e7df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200720%2FCLIQ5QRLZJ4R6XUU4MQIXTFR3U%2F&h=f79eec40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200720/CLIQ5QRLZJ4R6XUU4MQIXTFR3U/</a>"}]}